#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Ma soovin muuta mängu välimust. On see võimalik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. To change &bovo;'s visual theme you can use the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu> </"
#| "menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &bovo;'s visual theme you can use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> menu entry on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Jah. &bovo; teema muutmiseks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guisubmenu>Teema</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. The game of &bovo; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ei, &bovo;t ei saa mängida klaviatuuri abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No. There is no <quote>Save</quote> feature in &bovo; but &bovo; restores "
"the latest unfinished game on startup."
msgstr ""
"Ei, &bovo; ei paku <quote>salvestamise</quote> võimalust, kuid &bovo; "
"taastab käivitamisel viimase lõpetamata mängu seisu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where are the highscores?"
msgstr "Kus saab näha rekordeid?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "&bovo; does not have this feature."
msgstr "&bovo;l puudub selline võimalus."

